The paper proposes a novel method for density estimation of streaming and evolving data, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. The method is based on a dynamic basis approach and uses isometric log-ratio transformation to model and predict gradual monotonous changes in a distribution. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.ST (Statistics), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
